Spanish Cabinet Passes Wealth Tax as ‘Exceptional’ Measure

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-16T11:40:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/spanish-cabinet-passes-wealth-tax-as-exceptional-measure.html
Spain ’s Cabinet approved today the
reintroduction of a wealth tax as an “exceptional” measure,
Jose Blanco, the public works minister and government spokesman,
told reporters today in  Madrid . The measure was announced by
Finance Minister  Elena Salgado  yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  